{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"71b69351e2","title":"对设立国务院文化组请示报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af5fd381dc","index":0,"year":1970,"month":3,"day":13,"articleId":"71b69351e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"0d25802c12","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"71b69351e2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周恩来等1970年3月11日给毛泽东等写报告说，昨天中央政治局会议商定：一、在国务院之下设立一文化组，管理有关文艺、电影、出版、图书、博物等方面的工作。二、文化组的思想政治领导属中央政治局，政治局分工归中央文革；文化组的行政领导属国务院，党中央对该组的指示和决定，由国务院组织实施。三、文化组设组长、副组长和组员若千人，提议吴德为组长，刘贤权为副组长，石少华等7人为组员。四、文化组设一小的工作机构。毛泽东阅后，写了这个批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5cd0b5fb67","type":"title","text":"对设立国务院文化组请示报告的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"71b69351e2"},{"id":"0d25802c12","type":"paragraph","text":"同意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"71b69351e2"},{"id":"09ab021dd2","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十三日","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"71b69351e2"}],"page":{"id":"f67ab78229","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"71b69351e2","start":520,"end":520}}}},"__N_SSG":true}